<title>罗斯福的“四大自由”怎样改变世界？-海外网手机网</title>
<img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/imp?bid=0a673424000058df842b473700f39cf8&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54360298&amp;cid=32447&amp;mid=23621&amp;oid=4502&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;e=VOH7Jf0jKQGMpq0A4M5XO0PqE7lTwgYkQBvA8sobOPt6WOX0Zw0uXJJ11U7Syeh%2B&amp;k=65&amp;cb=3461452"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/opt?bid=0a673424000058df842b473700f39cf8&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54360298&amp;cid=32447&amp;mid=23621&amp;oid=4502&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;cb=56898602"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/imp?bid=0a671d61000358df842b70cf00ef2fc8&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54360299&amp;cid=32453&amp;mid=23627&amp;oid=1685&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;e=c0yL4DdhFvKGJgTPtIvipry2vGrXhJcxTlWud7luJiihrC9IWb23cQvnqiU3Z%2Fzm&amp;k=65&amp;cb=15333126"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/opt?bid=0a671d61000358df842b70cf00ef2fc8&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54360299&amp;cid=32453&amp;mid=23627&amp;oid=1685&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;cb=82062238"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/imp?bid=0a673423000058df842b4b0600f0d75e&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54348811&amp;cid=32449&amp;mid=23623&amp;oid=4502&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;e=eTvlHKAzAHKMpq0A4M5XO%2FaTvT8C2%2Bv7%2Bqj3PoWUmv5AA%2BI5M9mHiZgoJ6ZO86A9&amp;k=65&amp;cb=13128464"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/opt?bid=0a673423000058df842b4b0600f0d75e&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54348811&amp;cid=32449&amp;mid=23623&amp;oid=4502&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;cb=61579890"><img style="display: none; " src="http://afptrack.alimama.com/imp?bid=0a673424000058df842b473500f01a6e&amp;pid=mm_113716032_13558572_54360300&amp;cid=32450&amp;mid=23624&amp;oid=4502&amp;productType=1&amp;qytInfoMTime=1490983331&amp;e=QLnrJPXH19SMpq0A4M5XO0PqE7lTwgYkQBvA8s